Meta Mansions

8,888 unique digital mansions built on Ethereum as the core residency of the KEYS Metaverse.

Meta Mansions is more than an NFT; it's part of your identity.

Let's re-imagine the way we live, work, play, earn, and learn by creating the next wave of real estate and the KEYS Metaverse experience.

As a holder, you own 100% of your Meta Mansion. Please see terms here: https://keystoken.io/tos
